{"tid":1564101,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"《願榮光歸香港》2.0a","createTime":"2019-09-12T15:44:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T16:05:13.000Z","uid":101662,"like":5,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0c8f0db62a12e374f426cecb331bf11799e897b8","tid":1564101,"uid":101662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:44:52.000Z","msg":"見到有巴打幫國歌填咗新詞：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1555085/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1555085/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n我都手痕填咗個2.0a<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似有人話2.0啲字好深，我就偏向用字淺白嘅<br />\n另外尾段歌詞同原版有好大重疊，因為原版尾段實在太出色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />改到我都諗唔到點先可以再上一層樓<br />\n我改詞唔為取代原版，純粹作出自娛娛人，大家插得細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：毒撚一人創作，歌喉太差，唔錄音了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n齊奏 奏軍樂 立國旗<br />\n同歇盡性命 莫退避<br />\n憑鮮血直流 令決心堅厚<br />\n脫殖民必得拯救<br />\n<br />\n齊抗 抗宿命 復國仇<br />\n同破陣殺敵 寧莫退後<br />\n同火炮角力 亦誓要生死鬥<br />\n要壯烈一生不朽<br />\n<br />\n敵軍漸近 屠城殺戮<br />\n流熱血 更要聽身旁吶喊聲<br />\n要鍊成 全民族鬥志 長存續百世<br />\n勇抗 惡世 決永不滅<br />\n<br />\n黎民無數 應天命 已蘇醒<br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命<br />\n求全民擁抱自由 萬世都不朽<br />\n我願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人加油</span></span>"},{"pid":"581543e21955011f9f50f65887a90059678a2eee","tid":1564101,"uid":123991,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:45:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"dc14627cd55209c388293207e09df93a3ab3f67c","tid":1564101,"uid":185449,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:47:52.000Z","msg":"有種難以係街度唱出口同埋冇左果種振奮人心既感覺 建議你班2.0改歌撚咪再膠化件事 原版已經好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c002b9a36fce9a687ae1c7666b9e08e81105ca41","tid":1564101,"uid":40641,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:48:13.000Z","msg":"支持歌詞百花齊放！<br />\n如果有研究過各國國歌歷史，就知道改詞真係好閒"},{"pid":"3763c5247150ed0192b1130af5422838e5e9dac3","tid":1564101,"uid":70888,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:49:22.000Z","msg":"on撚9<br />\n改完有撚用咩？<br />\n咪撚係度分化<br />\n你d歌詞同中共首歌一鳩樣，打打一殺殺on9<br />\n連光復這香港 依句都無撚埋<br />\n唔該你慳返時間 做好文宣算<br />\nthanks"},{"pid":"4154ba8c632587e24f1bbad71c100e36d1e64968","tid":1564101,"uid":275677,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:49:28.000Z","msg":"可唔可以做左正經野先再推,做完正經野下星期一再比你慢慢J國歌"},{"pid":"b4493e8bc49eb7b8e391ec093b9f6260f6ddbe57","tid":1564101,"uid":101662,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3763c5247150ed0192b1130af5422838e5e9dac3","tid":1564101,"uid":70888,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:49:22.000Z","msg":"on撚9<br />\n改完有撚用咩？<br />\n咪撚係度分化<br />\n你d歌詞同中共首歌一鳩樣，打打一殺殺on9<br />\n連光復這香港 依句都無撚埋<br />\n唔該你慳返時間 做好文宣算<br />\nthanks"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:54:45.000Z","msg":"打打殺殺幾好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本場仗一路都係打打殺殺過嚟<br />\n<br />\n利申有瘋狂喺twitter做文宣"},{"pid":"d4e6f007d4e3759d9cbf9d0c197bb